{"tid":2100553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"01消息：今天最少新增47宗本地個案　至少10宗源頭","createTime":"2020-07-09T06:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T08:03:05.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a078ce3fdde3ba0742f9f385a0125f8e3fc0ddf","tid":2100553,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"本港昨天（8日）新增24宗新冠肺炎確診個案，當中19宗屬本地感染，5宗個案源頭不明。<br />\n<br />\n多宗個案與食肆有關，分別再有2宗涉及坪石彬記粥麵美食和3宗涉及佐敦新發茶餐廳的確診個案。慈雲山港泰護老中心成本港首間爆發疫情安老院，累計9名職員及院友確診。有確診患者是學生或學生家長，有學校自行停課，另外有4名患者是的士司機。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君直言是第三波爆發。<br />\n<br />\n疫情發展至今日，消息指自昨日記者會後，至今有約20宗確診或初步確診個案，當中有超過10宗屬本地個案；另外亦有消息指，政府最快今日公布收緊防疫措施，當中包括食肆將限制每檯最多8人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLBgfx3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLBgfx3.png&h=24ce87d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495677/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E47%E5%AE%97%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9110%E5%AE%97%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F495677%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E47%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%259110%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%258E%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=9f471b04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495677/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8